quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  63,9,O ona verit nie zmateny tvoj peniaze tvoj dieta zapamatat si GOD Those robit this bol losers
  63,10,Ona dat our provisions ona smrt pojdem ona potom ona say Moj Lord len Ona zdrzat this short chvila! Ja potom bol charitable join the righteous
  63,11,GOD never ZDRZAT appointed cas SMRT any soul. GOD JE fully Cognizant Z everything ONA ROBIT